data.description: Need an escape from the hustle and bustle of city life? This charming mid-century ranch style home is your desert oasis, nestled on the edge of 29 Palms right in the cusp of the breathtaking Mojave desert.    With 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, an open floor plan, and a sprawling wrap-around patio, this home seamlessly blends mid-century style with the natural beauty of the desert. As you take in views of the rugged Mojave landscape, you'll feel the stresses of everyday life slip away.      Spend sunny days lounging on the patio and taking in panoramic views of the surrounding desert, San Jacinto mountains, and Joshua Tree National Park's iconic landscapes. At night, stargazing from the patio is spectacular thanks to stunning dark skies.    The property offers total privacy and seclusion, with 8-foot fencing surrounding the perimeter. A detached garage provides ample storage for gear, with enough room left over for a workshop or artist studio.    Nearby attractions like Indian Cove and the wonders of Joshua Tree National Park are just a short drive away. And with the conveniences of 29 Palms minutes down the road, you'll have easy access to supplies whenever needed.    Don't miss this chance to own your own desert sanctuary! This special home offers the perfect blend of mid-century charm, privacy, and access to all the natural wonders the Mojave has to offer.
